Reasoning: The paper discusses the interlinking of language and visual understanding by machines, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the hope of achieving the old AI dream of building machines that could pass a Turing test, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper discusses the evaluation of different algorithms on open tasks, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
